== New Millchan version just dropped ==
https://anonfile.com/79R1c039n9/update_08chan_s_Millchan_version_201908141821_zip
Install instructions are inside.
Main features are:
- HUGE memory leaks fixed, board should be '''much''' faster now.
- This version is a debug build. While this means it might be a bit slower than a production build, it allows you to see all the code for the site and for the libraries the site is built on right in your browser's dev console.
Millchan's developer is also working on not blocking the browser's main thread, which should make the board even faster in the future.
